These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-1::.
There are 2 different nationalities: polish, dutch
The people use 2 different means of transport: subway, trike
1. the polish is on the left of the person driving the subway##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |
| Nationality   | polish  | dutch |
| Transport     | trike | subway  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-2::.
There 2 different types of food: eggplant, kiwi
The people have 2 different hobbies: magic-tricks, sudoku
1. the person eating kiwi is on the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |      2       |
| Food    | eggplant      | kiwi         |
| Hobby   | magic-tricks | sudoku |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-3::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: milk, soy-milk
The people have 2 different hobbies: magic-tricks, collecting
1. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2    |
| Beverage   | soy-milk | milk   |
| Hobby       | collecting  | magic-tricks |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-4::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  journalist, nurse
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: cycling, parkour
1. the nurse is on the right of the person who's sport is cycling##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |
| Job   | journalist  | nurse |
| Sport         | cycling | parkour    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-5::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, sprite
2 different games are played: mah-jongg, snooker
