.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-7::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: mystery, romance
The people have 2 different hobbies: dancing, writing
1. the person who's hobby is writing is on the right of the person watching mystery movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2     |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery | romance |
| Hobby      | dancing     | writing  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-8::.
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: baccarat, bongani
